21/09/2008
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- A military exercise dubbed "Adriatic Eagle 08" began at the Ilinden barracks in Skopje on Friday (September 19th). 
The ten-day exercise involves more than 100 members of special units from Macedonia, Albania and Croatia. 
Previous Adriatic Eagle exercises were held in Albania in 2006 and in Croatia in 2007. 
(MRT, MINA - 19/09/08)
